{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1488772, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "macos用用就习惯了", "timestamp": 1618924430, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488790, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "macos用用就会喜欢", "timestamp": 1618924580, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "macOS有完整的office三件套，基本使用没问题", "timestamp": 1618924600, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488804, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "macos虽然也不错，但是7000块的mac应该不太行......", "timestamp": 1618924696, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488811, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488804, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 买m1的mba性能足够的", "timestamp": 1618924721, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488816, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "小新pro14主流是5000多块吧", "timestamp": 1618924750, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488844, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "刚入了mba m1，体验极佳，强推", "timestamp": 1618924985, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488851, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488811, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯，但起码也得上512G存储的，现在笔记本都标配512G了。", "timestamp": 1618925024, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488858, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488851, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 价格++++\n现在用128Gmbp贼难受", "timestamp": 1618925057, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488862, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "实际上macos用到现在，并不怎么喜欢。窗口调节、触摸板操作的便捷程度都不如win10", "timestamp": 1618925074, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488862, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 触控板不如win你是认真的么", "timestamp": 1618925102, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488865, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 是啊，win10可以三指切换窗口。这个大概看个人使用习惯？", "timestamp": 1618925147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488883, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488871, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 操作上可能各有优劣吧，但是触控手感Mac那是无人能敌", "timestamp": 1618925222, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488816, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 小新i7的话大概7000多", "timestamp": 1618925285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488898, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488883, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哦你说硬件的手感，那mbp确实不错", "timestamp": 1618925318, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488912, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488898, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: macOS其实有很多触控板手势的，可以在设置里面看到", "timestamp": 1618925369, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488915, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488895, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 以我去年九月买电脑悲惨经历，建议千万别买联想，直接加点钱mbp", "timestamp": 1618925384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488921, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488912, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 仔细研究过，结论是不如win10方便。win10也很多手势设置哦", "timestamp": 1618925430, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488930, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488816, "tag": null, "text": "没用过mac请教下各位，我用Windows经常为了逃避软件付费，经常淘宝软件，自己装。（非常不好意思）\n用了mac的话，还可以这样干吗？ipad想下载某些软件的话只能在app store上付费，好难受", "timestamp": 1618925475, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488943, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488930, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: MacBook不用，其他地方下载的软件当然可以装", "timestamp": 1618925513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488959, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488921, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 嗯嗯，没怎么用过windows，更别说有触控板的windows了（", "timestamp": 1618925578, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488969, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Mac有个优势：可以下载树洞客户端（", "timestamp": 1618925607, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488930, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 但是有些软件压根没开发mac版的，如果专业要经常用到这样的软件，不建议mac", "timestamp": 1618925618, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488977, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488972, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对，特别是仿真软件", "timestamp": 1618925636, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果打算长久用，那就买Mac。macOS有许多局限性，但是用用你也就习惯了，大部分的学习和工作软件，都可以找到alternative，少数非常局限的软件，估计也不会是高频软件/可以用虚拟机，或者Boot Camp来搞定。如果硬盘小，还可以用高速外挂硬盘装个windows go。再不行，还可以去图书感嘛～\n\n如果打算用几年就换机器，那还是买PC吧，你无需适应新的用户习惯，不需要考虑学习成本。想要的盗版随手可得，想玩的游戏全部兼容，还不挑配件，买个低配回来自己换内存换固态硬盘，能省不少钱。但是，你依然要考虑隔三差五为它杀毒、清理、升级补丁，或用个一年半载可能就得重装下系统等等，当个大爷伺候着。\n\n各有各的优缺点，看你更在乎哪一点吧。", "timestamp": 1618925665, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488992, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好的我准备入mac了，请问最少买哪个版本的mac能够日常需求？文科生最多跑跑python了", "timestamp": 1618925712, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1488997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488992, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 文科生的话无脑m1的MacBook Air", "timestamp": 1618925741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489014, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "macOS和windows的区别，类似手机iOS和Android的区别。\n\nAndroid自由度高，硬件性能好，但总是有些隐私顾虑、广告泛滥、越用越卡顿的烦恼。装了加速软件，却殊不知是各种手机关机和加速清理工具，拖慢了你的手机。\n\niOS限制太多，不能随便装软件，但保证了系统的安全，诈骗犯发个木马，你没点基础知识，还装不上。iPhone硬件也是各种鸡肋，祖传5V1A，还贵的要死。但好处在是你在用手机，而不是手机在用你。", "timestamp": 1618925873, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489026, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1488997, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 对，就直接上M1吧，虽然目前有些软件兼容性不好，但放心好了，大厂都会跟上来的。", "timestamp": 1618925977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就没有找到7000块的小新pro14，是MX450独显版的，而且涨价了？现在最值得买的是它的标压锐龙版，是核显，5500左右；yoga14s与其基本一致，升级了屏幕。", "timestamp": 1618926013, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489107, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 对独显", "timestamp": 1618926472, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489113, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489036, "tag": null, "text": "mba m1   8g 512g，应该够了吧，大概8000元的样子", "timestamp": 1618926529, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489113, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对dz这种情况应该够了", "timestamp": 1618926545, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489113, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我建议内存大点哦，16G吧……", "timestamp": 1618926913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489169, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489113, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 硬盘小可以外挂，内存是换不了的。", "timestamp": 1618926946, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489169, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 8G和16G在不是特别重度的使用差别其实不明显，就看洞主有没有这样的使用场景了，比如同时开几十个标签页\n\n不过想用得久的话还是建议16G", "timestamp": 1618927060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489289, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还是安利一下yoga14s锐龙核显，这个好像和mba更接近😂减些钱买更精细的屏幕，16G+512G，更多的接口。", "timestamp": 1618928218, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489398, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "出国+文科 必选mac 可以等等今晚发布会", "timestamp": 1618929019, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489427, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我是#279456 的olivia，强烈建议别买macbook", "timestamp": 1618929220, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489462, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489427, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: mac上的office确实不好用，不过平时都latex了用的不多", "timestamp": 1618929503, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489468, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489462, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 用Mac的话强烈推荐用Keynote来替代PowerPoint，动画超赞", "timestamp": 1618929558, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489473, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489462, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: office确实渣", "timestamp": 1618929575, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489613, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用mac版的word写完docx，发给老师修改，你能保证没有格式问题吗？", "timestamp": 1618930597, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1489616, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1489613, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 没有问题的", "timestamp": 1618930610, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1490633, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Windows的话为什么不考虑yoga呢", "timestamp": 1618936916, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1490635, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且联想全球服务站不比苹果少吧", "timestamp": 1618936954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1490656, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1490635, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 国行不全球联保吧似乎", "timestamp": 1618937166, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1490661, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1490656, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 建议百度或咨询客服", "timestamp": 1618937233, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496971, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哈哈 又一个买mac的文科生", "timestamp": 1619007457, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我确实佩服苹果的营销", "timestamp": 1619007471, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1496989, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从实用角度买mac只有两类人，码农、设计师，其他学科方向基本不存在macOS的优势地位", "timestamp": 1619007603, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1501226, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1496989, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason:请问 为什么码农用mac比win好啊，感觉程序员不是要装很多软件配置IDE之类的吗，苹果不是封闭性太好不利于这些吗", "timestamp": 1619066623, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1508112, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1501226, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可以区分command+c和ctrl+c", "timestamp": 1619113753, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1508249, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 292811, "reply_to": 1508112, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 草，真实", "timestamp": 1619115581, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 15, "pid": 292811, "reply": 54, "tag": null, "text": "求问联想小新pro14和macbook13.3，哪个更好？\ndz女孩子比较喜欢13.3存小屏幕的轻薄本\n看了两款都是7000多\n之前一直用的windows系统，担心iOS装各种软件啊用office比较麻烦——这么看选小新pro比较好\n大四准备出国了，担心保修问题——这么看选mac比较好\n好纠结啊......", "timestamp": 1618924165, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1619115583, "url": "", "vote": {}}}